    • Constructor Detail

      • GuildSettings

        public GuildSettings()
        Constructs a new GuildSettings object with the following default values.
        • prefix: !
        • ignoreCase: true
        • ignoreBots: true
        • parseQuotes: true
        • helpLabels: help
        • mutedChannels: none
        • isMutedGuild: false
        • maxDistance: 3

      • GuildSettings

        public GuildSettings​(long guildId,
                     @NotNull
                     @NotNull String prefix,
                     boolean ignoreCase,
                     boolean ignoreBots,
                     boolean parseQuotes,
                     @NotNull
                     @NotNull Set<String> helpLabels,
                     @NotNull
                     @NotNull Set<Long> mutedChannels,
                     boolean isMutedGuild,
                     int maxDistance)
        Constructs a new GuildSettings object.
        Parameters:
        guildId - the guild id
        prefix - the prefix to use
        ignoreCase - whether to ignore the case
        ignoreBots - whether to ignore the case
        parseQuotes - whether to concatenate quotes, e.g. foo "quote string" bar -> ["foo", "quote string", "bar"]
        helpLabels - a set of all help labels
        mutedChannels - a set of muted channels
        isMutedGuild - whether this guild should be ignored completely
        maxDistance - the maximal Levenshtein distance to use when routing commands
